{"tid":1206012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「呢一刻，香港唔可以冇左我」","createTime":"2019-06-12T01:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T01:03:58.000Z","uid":32722,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a45d3d8ee44cdc8ef10fd2dfd087269484d43dd","tid":1206012,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"尋日下晝，有個後生仔遞左張假紙俾我。<br />\n<br />\n然後講左上面個一句說話。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢講，公司有個政策，一日病假係可以唔洗假紙。小心保重。<br />\n<br />\n跟住我係度諗，佢呢一句既份量可能係我人生中聽過最重既。<br />\n<br />\n有佢可否推倒惡法？唔知。冇佢係咪就一定唔會成功？唔知。<br />\n<br />\n我淨係知道，如果每一個人都係咁諗既話，香港點會冇未來？<br />\n<br />\n警隊編制三萬幾，香港動員到三十萬人圍立法會，你仲要驚警犬？尋晚金鐘站就話你知，警犬圍你，你夠多人圍番佢轉頭，暴政必亡。<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家記住，呢一刻，香港唔可以冇左我。"},{"pid":"f2adb07364dc449c835362abbc8d5d1d4e3e207b","tid":1206012,"uid":216975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2da0595fbe347cbe82a9e008490372823bc0645","tid":1206012,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9b07992ea39fb0e96b0e5365e1a2537641e5ee","tid":1206012,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}